## CSS Layout Cheat Sheet

### Flexbox
```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;        /* or column */
  justify-content: center;   /* main axis: flex-start|center|space-between|space-around */
  align-items: center;       /* cross axis: stretch|flex-start|center|flex-end */
  flex-wrap: wrap;           /* allow wrapping */
  gap: 1rem;                 /* space between items */
}
.item {
  flex: 1;            /* grow to fill space */
  flex-basis: 200px;  /* minimum width */
  flex-shrink: 0;     /* don't shrink */
}
```

### CSS Grid
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);  /* 3 equal columns */
  grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr 300px;  /* sidebar, main, right */
  grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;       /* header, content, footer */
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.item {
  grid-column: 1 / 3;    /* span 2 columns */
  grid-row: 1 / -1;      /* full height */
}
```

### Responsive (Media Queries)
```css
/* Mobile-first approach */
.grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }  /* 1 column on mobile */

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }  /* 2 on tablet */
}
@media (min-width: 1200px) {
  .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }  /* 4 on desktop */
}
```

### Centering Tricks
```css
/* Perfect center with flexbox */
.center { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
/* Full-page centered content */
.full-center { display: grid; place-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
```
